@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AI MODULE - Artificial Intelligence Features
### ============================================

### RAG - Query Knowledge Base
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/rag-query
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How to optimize database queries?",
  "context": "database"
}

### RAG - Ingest Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/rag-ingest
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentId": "doc-uuid",
  "content": "Database optimization guide content..."
}

### RAG - Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/rag-search?q=optimization&limit=10
Authorization: {{token}}

### CHAT - AI Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How can I improve my sales process?",
  "context": "sales"
}

### AI MODE - Get/Set AI Mode
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/mode
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - RAG: Retrieval Augmented Generation
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
